Package: auto-temp-ctrl
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-venv, python3-pip, libgpiod2 (>= 2.1.3)
Description: Auto temperature-based GPIO control wrapper
 This package provides a system wrapper and service for auto starting and managing the auto_temp_gpiod_ctrl Python package, with configuration and management commands.
